    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you hit with your Sneak Attack on the first round of a combat, the target must succeed on a Constitution saving throw (DC 8 plus your Dexterity modifier and Proficiency Bonus), or the attack's damage is doubled against the target.</p><section id=\"secret-BnFwQLxoe98cX89P\" class=\"secret\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The <strong>Death Strike</strong> activity includes the save and your normal Sneak Attack damage.</p><p>With the target selected you can either right click on the damage roll's chat card and select <span class=\"reference\"><em class=\"fas fa-user-injured\"></em>Apply Double Damage</span> or click the \"2\" button and then the <span class=\"reference\"><em class=\"fa-solid fa-reply-all\"></em>Apply</span> button.</p></section>",
